'''Bujumbura''' d tamaneɣt n tmurt n [[Burundi]]. Zedɣen-tt 235.440 n yimezdaɣen. D nettat ay d tamdint tameqrant akk deg Burundi.
Tezga-d deg ugafa-agmuḍan (nord-est) n ugelmim afriqi n [[Tanganyika]]. Deg Bujumbura ay d-yezga usagen (lmerṣa) ameqran n Burundi, yerna seg usagen-a ay tessuffuɣ tmurt-a ɣer beṛṛa lɣella-nnes n [[lqahwa]], leqḍen, [[igelman]] akked [[Ahallun|uhallun]] (étain).
